@startuml

state "Game Started" as Start
state "Game In Progress" as Progress
state "Player's Turn" as PlayerTurn
state "Game Over" as End

[*] --> Start

Start --> Progress : New game or Join game
Progress --> PlayerTurn : Player makes a move
PlayerTurn --> Progress : Valid move played
PlayerTurn --> End : Game over (no valid moves or full board)
Progress --> End : Both players passed

End --> [*] : Game ended

@enduml